                ------ ab ---] <lb n="2"/>Tropaiophoro <supplied reason="lost">Hercule</supplied> <lb n="3"/>fratre <supplied reason="lost">divi Commodi <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="4"/>ex <expan><abbr>provinc</abbr><ex>ia</ex></expan> Pannonia <supplied reason="lost">inferiore</supplied> <lb n="5"/>in amplissimum ordinem <lb n="6"/>adsumpto <supplied reason="lost" cert="low">Ulpius</supplied><supplied reason="lost">Ulpius</supplied> <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>praef</abbr><ex>ectus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>coh</abbr><ex>ortis</ex></expan> &amp;lt;VII&amp;gt; Br&amp;lt;e&amp;gt;ucorum <lb n="8"/>equites <expan><abbr>singular</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> eius
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Nur handschriftllich überliefert. Bei dem Geehrten handelt es sich vielleicht um Sex. Varius Marcellus (PIR V 192).</p>
